Allowed libraries (use these consistently):
- Animations: framer-motion (preferred for scroll/hover/in-view).
- Icons: lucide-react ONLY (do not use react-icons).
- i18n: i18next + react-i18next + i18next-browser-languagedetector.
- Smooth scroll: @studio-freight/lenis.
- Class utils: clsx + tailwind-merge (prefer a cn() helper).
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + custom CSS for liquid glass.

Do NOT introduce:
- UI kits (MUI/Chakra/shadcn).
- Routers (React Router/Next Router).
- Email/form libraries (EmailJS, Formik, React Hook Form).
- State management libs (Redux/Zustand) unless explicitly requested.

Implementation preferences:
- Use functional components + TypeScript.
- Use framer-motion's whileInView/viewport for reveal animations.
